{"tid":810242,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手第七日，頹足七日","createTime":"2018-09-07T19:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T19:54:39.000Z","uid":183368,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"717a6c73b11b78526bf049f86237b5e9721671b6","tid":810242,"uid":183368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:33:49.000Z","msg":"兩年幾嘅感情，說散就散...<br />\n<br />\n我自己一個人租樓住，間屋係同佢一齊揀嘅...<br />\n雖然唔係同居，但係佢差唔多日日都會上嚟...<br />\n呢家，剩返自己一個喺呢間屋... 不斷閃起佢嘅畫面..<br />\n<br />\n好頹廢...<br />\n有機衫喺分手日洗左，到呢家都未拎岀嚟掠乾...<br />\n雪櫃有一堆分手前買嘅餸，分手後一直都冇攞過岀嚟，呢家已經過哂期...<br />\n有堆污糟碗碟，喺分手日放左喺sink盤... 今日都未洗...<br />\n垃圾自從分手日後都冇掉過...<br />\n<br />\n完全冇哂動力... 每日食得半餐飯，冇胃口...<br />\n原來已經瘦左8磅...<br />\n<br />\n成世人都未試過咁頹...<br />\n究竟呢段日子仲要捱幾耐..."},{"pid":"bdfcbd39bd042329e3894d7bdce16499b7d94b00","tid":810242,"uid":107649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:34:50.000Z","msg":"返多啲工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b81fcdf19677ab268edd7acb1fe4a76bc0fd31b","tid":810242,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到都好sad 搵下朋友陪"},{"pid":"3d135dbf0cff65624f1ff933e58d15cc3d9fde30","tid":810242,"uid":100767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:36:28.000Z","msg":"樓主幾歲"},{"pid":"9f88e039deacc4396fcd680c595c20addb458f4f","tid":810242,"uid":183368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b81fcdf19677ab268edd7acb1fe4a76bc0fd31b","tid":810242,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到都好sad 搵下朋友陪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:38:42.000Z","msg":"我朋友見倒我都謝哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都好盡力陪我... <br />\n但一日廿四小時，friend 都有嘢做嘅...<br />\n<br />\n只要係自己一個嘅時候，尤其是返到屋企就.... <img src=